reviewText: Excellent movie.  Great stars and plot.
product was delivered promptly and we've enjoyed the movies
Good movie set.  Tab that holds the DVD was broken and disc was sliding all over the place.  Small scratch, but does not seem to bother the playing of the disc.
Keeping family close even thou there may be issues.
Loved all of the movies on this set.  My favorite movie was Thicker Than Water.  Melissa Gilbert has always been my favorite actress since Little House on the Prairie.
Love Hallmark Movies.  Faith and family values - not shown enough in today's world.
